Press the Select Character Button to choose a character to play with or press the Options button to adjust the settings.
The Select Character button will bring a screen to choose the character. After choosing a character, there will be a dialog
sequence that can be skipped. 
Each character can move and has 4 abilities (1 movement ability, 1 heal ability, and 2 offensive/defensive abilities). The
keybindings can be adjusted as needed. Fight off as many waves as possible!